<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .wrapper {
            background-color: #00205c;
            padding: 0 0;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 600px;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
        }
        .email-container {
            border-top: 2px solid #000000;
            padding-bottom: 1px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #00205c;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
        .header img {
            position: relative;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-top: -10px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #385c93;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p strong {
            color: #F33;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .red-text{
            color:#ff2121;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        a {
            color: #00205c;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .doubleUnderline {
            text-decoration:underline;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #385c93;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Background Wrapper -->
    <div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <!-- Email Header -->
            <div class="header">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dg2rwod7i/image/upload/v1725984104/xemwtvs7obkdedgyamh1.png" alt="Popular logo">
            </div>
    
            <!-- Email Body -->
            <div class="email-container">
                <div class="content">
                    <p>Hi <span class="red-text">{!Case.Account_First_Name__c} {!Case.Account_Last_Name__c}</span>:</p>
                    <p>
                        Please accept our heartfelt condolences during this difficult time. 
                        We are here to offer our full support. We have carefully reviewed your 
                        Liquidation Funds request associated with ticket <span class="red-text">{!Case.CaseNumber}</span>, 
                        and we are pleased to inform you that it has been approved. Your check is 
                        now available for pick-up at our <span class="red-text">{!Case.Branch_Name__c}</span> branch in <span class="red-text">{!Case.Branch_Town__c}</span>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We kindly ask you to bring a valid form of identification and mention the ticket number upon arrival. 
                        If there's anything more we can do to assist you, please don't hesitate to reach out
                    </p>
                    <p>We are here to serve you;<br>
                    Banco Popular de Puerto Rico
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>